{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM07_120.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x20,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "I hope it was just a groundless fear..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hey wait, Plachta. Why are you rushing so much? Can you explain it to me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Right... I need to tell you about this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "...You aren't the only one seeking the \"Cauldron of Knowledge\"."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "There have been some, patiently waiting all this time, for a chance to obtain the Cauldron."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Wait, really!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Yes. It's a device with such enormous power. It would only be natural for there to be many people seeking it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Well... Now that you mention it, that makes sense."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "However, among them, there are two who especially mustn't be allowed to obtain it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1c,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "...Meklet and Atomina. They must not have the Cauldron."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x26,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Wait, those two!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x27,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "It's true that they mentioned the \"Cauldron of Knowledge\" before... But why not?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1d,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Those two likely seek to use the Cauldron to return to their previous form."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "The form of an alchemist, from my time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x28,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "What... Do you mean?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "500 years ago, I fought a certain alchemist."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "His name at the time was Luard... The true form of Meklet and Atomina."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "During the battle 500 years ago, I fought Luard, and emerged victorious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Then, I split and sealed his soul away in two bodies, artificial lifeforms called Meklet and Atomina."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "You talked about artificial lifeforms before. They're the ones that are \"human, yet not human\", right...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yes. They possess eternal life, as \"objects\" resembling humans. That is their true identity."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "So why do they want the \"Cauldron of Knowledge\"?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Their bodies, created through alchemy, cannot use alchemy themselves."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "That's why it's impossible for them to use alchemy to return to their former self."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "However... Tell me, what would happen if they had the \"Cauldron of Knowledge\"?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "If the \"Cauldron of Knowledge\" lets anyone use alchemy... Even they would be able to use it...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Exactly. Using the Cauldron, they could return to their true form. That is their desire."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Normally, since they cannot create the Key of Truth, coming here would be impossible for them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "...Oh, I see. This is because I made the Key of Truth..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "...No, this isn't your fault. If only I had remembered this sooner...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Plachta..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "If those two obtain the \"Cauldron of Knowledge\", it would become a grave situation. We need to hurry."
        }
    ]
}